headline: Humana Announces 2026 Medicare Advantage Plans Designed with Veterans in Mind
summary: LOUISVILLE, Ky., October 21, 2025--Humana announces 2026 Medicare Advantage plans designed with veterans in mind. Humana USAA Honor Giveback Plans elevate mental health support.
